sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Streamlit as Streamlit UI
    participant BrowserApp
    participant BrowserHistory
    participant DatabaseManager
    participant SQLite

    User->>Streamlit: Enter URL & click Visit
    Streamlit->>BrowserApp: visit(url)
    BrowserApp->>BrowserHistory: insert(url)
    BrowserHistory->>BrowserHistory: Create Node, set prev/next
    BrowserHistory->>BrowserHistory: Delete forward history
    BrowserHistory-->>BrowserApp: Node
    BrowserApp->>DatabaseManager: save_history(urls, current)
    DatabaseManager->>SQLite: DELETE + INSERT rows
    SQLite-->>DatabaseManager: OK
    DatabaseManager-->>BrowserApp: Done
    BrowserApp-->>Streamlit: True
    Streamlit-->>User: Display updated UI

    User->>Streamlit: Click Back
    Streamlit->>BrowserApp: back()
    BrowserApp->>BrowserHistory: back()
    BrowserHistory->>BrowserHistory: current = current.prev
    BrowserHistory-->>BrowserApp: current Node
    BrowserApp->>DatabaseManager: save_history(urls, current)
    DatabaseManager->>SQLite: Update is_current
    SQLite-->>DatabaseManager: OK
    BrowserApp-->>Streamlit: current URL
    Streamlit-->>User: Display current page
